      <title>律师团体呼吁改革以简化美国设立新银行的流程</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/lawyer-group-urges-overhaul-us-bank-charter-process-encourage-new-entrants-2025-01-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一群律师在致银行机构新任领导层的一封信中写道，美国监管机构必须简化设立新银行的授权流程，强调该行业需要适应金融科技时代。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/lawyer-group-urges-overhaul-us-bank-charter-process-encourage-new-entrants-2025-01-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 07:45:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着 Signa 清算范围扩大，瑞士宝盛集团董事长将离职</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/julius-baer-chairman-romeo-lacher-step-down-2025-01-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士宝盛银行 (Julius Baer) 周一宣布，该银行董事长罗密欧·拉赫尔 (Romeo Lacher) 将卸任。该银行一年前因涉足破产的房地产集团 Signa 而遭受重大损失后，继续进行管理层改组。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/julius-baer-chairman-romeo-lacher-step-down-2025-01-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 07:05:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
