      <title>特朗普阴影下：欧洲央行面临的五个问题</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/trumps-shadow-five-questions-ecb-2025-01-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行周四举行唐纳德·特朗普上任以来的首次会议，美国关税威胁令欧元区低迷的经济面临威胁，并可能使经济前景复杂化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/trumps-shadow-five-questions-ecb-2025-01-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 05:12:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
